{"tid":1386020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IFC 真係一個行街既好地方","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T10:30:29.000Z","uid":167329,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3b234dbd10d81d6f9ea458e26e6aa65cdcfb9ce1","tid":1386020,"uid":167329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:32:44.000Z","msg":"身為香港重要地標既IFC<br />\n有齊唔同既<span style=\"color: red;\">外資零售業</span><br />\n可以比我地睇下外國既商品<br />\n上面既寫字樓又多<span style=\"color: red;\">國企</span><br />\n比我地感受一下祖國既繁榮<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">遊客</span>又多 比我地練習下重要既普通話<br />\n又有良好既冷氣系統 又係室內<br />\n唔怕令人<span style=\"color: red;\">眼濕濕既氣體</span>進入 <br />\n有足夠既水源 飲品 <br />\n完全用唔到<span style=\"color: red;\">水車</span>既作用<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連接地鐵 3條線 2個站</span><br />\n去邊到都咁方便<br />\n點解仲要去外面行街呢<br />\n又哂又熱 仲要買水車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b290ff137d22fdc4d532a0909b959cae15ba3b8d","tid":1386020,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"IFC 機場<br />\n<br />\n天氣不似預期, 但要走總要飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658e9f12c2a85025b47b889ac2c855e23b47d993","tid":1386020,"uid":167329,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b290ff137d22fdc4d532a0909b959cae15ba3b8d","tid":1386020,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"IFC 機場<br />\n<br />\n天氣不似預期, 但要走總要飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:38:30.000Z","msg":"入一次機場太貴了<br />\n一來一回都50 巴士又少<br />\n機鐵太貴"},{"pid":"f7c2424e0e8790b8e2274507226fcbed38714dc1","tid":1386020,"uid":273272,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:38:46.000Z","msg":"仲要同沙田新城市一樣，係新鴻基"},{"pid":"fb6819617b11cfba645c7fafa39c2aeea531b611","tid":1386020,"uid":273272,"like":2,"disl